<br>
A number of original LoS founders and members are still about in various forms - some still in the League, and some in other forms or pursuing other goals.  I'm asking all the old-timers to reach back in your memories and, if you were associated with the LoS, see if you can think of any dates and significant events.  Once I started keeping Didi's diary most events are dated but before that I do not have any information.<br>
<br>
Do you know any dates for the below, or any other events of significance?<br>
<br>
Founding of the League of Shadows (leader: Jaynus - who were co-founders and original officers?)<br>
<br>
Handover of leadership to Lord Gray<br>
<br>
Any early raids of note?  I know that back in the early days, LoS and FnF were neck and neck exploring those new zones!<br>
<br>
When was our alliance to the Blackened Roses formed (and when did they disband)?<br>
<br>
Were there any other guild alliances back then?<br>
<br>
Were there any guild wars?  (I believe Apep left to form Ebon Storm and promising the downfall of the LoS at one point, but am not sure when this happened or exactly what was said?)<br>
<br>
Etc...<br>
<br>
Any memories, particularly ones with dates, would be appreciated for the sake of history! <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><br>
